    Hell Beast emerged from the CR chamber repaird. Gremlin then led him out 
of the chamber room and into the bridge, where Tarantulas, Tankkor, Rampage, 
Paralysis, and Aerostreak wirly looked at them.
    "Ah, these are the troops of Black Aracnia. I see....not much to work 
with but we will make the best of it." Hell Beast said making his way around 
the room. It was differently arrangened from the last time he was here.
    Aracnia marched in and glared at Hell Beast. "Im in control of this ship! 
Argh! While your here you are under my influence and will follow my orders, 
understand? Because if you refuse to do so, I have 7 bots who will blow you 
bit to bit." 
    Hell Beast frowned. She was being a bitch, and it would be easyer if 
things went this way because she would let them get away with things if he 
was serving her. "Alright, your wish is my command."
